### BudgetExercise
Champs :
- id
- clientId
- name
- code
- startDate
- endDate
- status
- createdAt
- updatedAt

Relations :
- Client
- Budget[]

Contraintes :
- `@@unique([clientId, code])`
- `@@index([clientId])`
- `@@index([status])`

